column3: Hmm.. is this a complete transition to namespaceless of the whole QT part? If not, what is the reason to only adapt these files?\nThe PR itself looks good to me but i would also say that this is a "no-code" change and could go in over trivial@theuni.\n
This covers the whole Qt part!\n
Verified that this removes all `using namespace` from the GUI implementation files. Which is not terribly useful, it's mostly important to avoid it in _headers_ but anyhow. utACK.\n
